metadata.name: Sunset Highway
metadata.description: I was at this location looking for compositions facing east to capture the alignment of the crescent moon with five planets during moonrise the next morning. As I was packing up I noticed a storm brewing  in the west. I set up my camera and waited for some cars to pass through the highway below. After almost an hour I got the light trails I was looking for.
